<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-4840] Overlay doesn&apos;t work properly when page is rotated</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4840</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Reverse of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4596&quot; title=&quot;Overlays with /Rotate value appear rotated in result file&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-4596&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-4596&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, when the base page is rotated but not the overlay. Whatever needs to be done will probably be in&#160;&lt;tt&gt;calculateAffineTransform()&lt;/tt&gt; or in &lt;tt&gt;createOverlayXObject()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
